review:
Visited Dr. Abhishek Vaish for my mom's severe elbow pain. My mom's have had an operation few years back but it didn't go well because of that her elbow got dislocated. It was her working hand and she wasn't even able to hold any stuff and bend her arms. We tried several doctors due the pain my mother was having for months but Mr. Abhishek Vaish diagnosed the problem accurately, did a surgery for elbow dislocation and it did the wonders. 
I highly recommend Dr. Abhishek Vaish for his strengths in the field and his professionalism.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: My son had an accident and was limping, we went to 2 different NHS trusts in London two times and no one picked up his problem. We spoke to Dr Vaish who reviewed the X-ray and provided us with the initial diagnosis, moreover, he guided us on how to get an orthopedic consultant’s opinion in London. Without his kind help, we wouldn’t have known about our son’s chronic hip problem that needed follow-up for years. Thank you forever Dr. Abhishek Vaish
